# ---- Local sweep + worker output ----
# Broader glob: catches dydx-*-results.json (one of which embedded a testnet
# wallet mnemonic) and any future *-results.json the scripts emit. Keep
# specific filenames below as safety belt if the glob is ever loosened.
docs/*-results.json
docs/test-results.json
docs/coinbase-test-results.json
docs/kalshi-test-results.json

